+    id: "h6",
+    text: `ERBB2 dependency is strongest in cell lines where ${erbb2Pair.a.pred.text} and ${erbb2Pair.b.pred.text}; this subgroup has more negative \`dependency_ERBB2\` than other cell lines.`,
